OL,4,Cservice have 'full support' says
OL,5,Cminister
OL,7,FThe Welsh Government minister
OL,8,Foverseeing the management of the
OL,9,Ftroubled South Wales Fire and Rescue
OL,10,FService says the commissioners
OL,11,Fappointed to oversee reform have her
OL,12,F"full support".
OL,14,FDeputy Minister for Social Partnership
OL,15,FHannah Blythyn has spoken for the
OL,16,Ffirst time since ITV Wales reported
OL,17,Fthat the fire chief brought in to head
OL,18,Fup the service is himself at the
OL,19,Fcentre of bullying allegations.
