OL,7,FHannah Blythyn announced the
OL,8,Fappointment of four commissioners on 6
OL,9,FFebruary after a 'damning' independent
OL,10,Freport exposed a culture of sexism and
OL,11,Fmisogyny.
OL,13,FThe deputy minister today told ITV
OL,14,FWales: "The commissioners have our
OL,15,Ffull support. I have confidence in
OL,16,Fthem to take this forward."
OL,18,FShe acknowledged the scale of the
OL,19,Fchallenge saying "It's complex" and
OL,20,F"not going to be easy".
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/11
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
