OL,7,FBut Ms Blythyn added: "We will make
OL,8,Fsure we work with them (commissioners)
OL,9,Fto make sure we get what we need in
OL,10,Ffuture for the service and the
OL,11,Fcommunities in Wales."
OL,13,FThe FBU union was "shocked" to hear of
OL,14,FMr Millington's appointment at the
OL,15,Fstart of the month and has questioned
OL,16,Fwhether "due diligence" was done.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/11
