OL,7,FThe deputy minister responded by
OL,8,Fsaying "It is the commissioners' remit
OL,9,Fto appoint new management" and that it
OL,10,Fwas their decision "under advice to
OL,11,Fappoint an interim chair".
OL,13,FWhen asked at what stage she knew
OL,14,Fabout the claims faced by Mr
OL,15,FMillington and the tribunal process,
OL,16,FMs Blythyn said: "It's not for me to
OL,17,Fcomment on an ongoing process".
