OL,7,FShe quickly turned her attention to
OL,8,Fthe challenges facing South Wales Fire
OL,9,Fand Rescue Service (SWFRS) paying
OL,10,Ftribute to the people who contributed
OL,11,Fto the independent review.
OL,13,FThe deputy minister said: "Those women
OL,14,Fand whistleblowers came forward so
OL,15,Faction was taken at SWFRS and we
OL,16,Fcontinue to support anyone else coming
OL,17,Fforward and try to change culture for
OL,18,Fgood in the future.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/11
