OL,7,F"I think the first thing we need to do
OL,8,Fis step back and realise why we are in
OL,9,Fthese circumstances and that we took
OL,10,Fas a Government unprecedented action
OL,11,Fand used the fullest extent of our
OL,12,Fpowers to intervene in SWFRS after the
OL,13,FFenella Morris KC report which we all
OL,14,Fagreed was damning.
OL,16,F"There was support for that
OL,17,Fintervention and we put forward
OL,18,Findependent commissioners in place and
OL,19,Fthose four have had to act.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/11
