OL,7,F"They have acted and they have our
OL,8,Fsupport to act in terms of the chief
OL,9,Fhas gone and they have needed to put
OL,10,Fan interim chief in to ensure
OL,11,Foperational continuity."
OL,13,FMs Blythyn says the issues highlighted
OL,14,Fin the South Wales Fire and Rescue
OL,15,FService culture report, go "beyond the
OL,16,Ffire service".
OL,18,FShe added: "There is no place immune
OL,19,Ffrom this. I've worked in places where
OL,20,Fit has happened."
