OL,7,F"We are working with the commissioners
OL,8,Fand supporting them to bring that
OL,9,Fchange through and we want to see that
OL,10,Fhappen in full."
OL,12,FSouth Wales Fire and Rescue Service
OL,13,Fcommissioner Vin Randeniya has today
OL,14,Fconfirmed for the first time that the
OL,15,Fcommissioners knew about Stuart
OL,16,FMillington's forthcoming employment
OL,17,Ftribunal.
