OL,7,FMr Randeniya said: "The process
OL,8,Finvolved approaching several senior
OL,9,Findividuals within the other Welsh
OL,10,Ffire and rescue services, and testing
OL,11,Ftheir experience, skills, and
OL,12,Favailability against several
OL,13,Fprerequisites agreed by the
OL,14,FCommissioners.
OL,16,F"The commissioners collectively
OL,17,Fdecided that Stuart Millington met
OL,18,Fthose requirements, and he has been
OL,19,Ftransferred on a secondment basis to
OL,20,FSouth Wales Fire and Rescue Service as
OL,21,FInterim Chief Fire Officer.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G9/11
