OL,7,F"All commissioners were aware of
OL,8,FInterim CFO Millington's record and
OL,9,Fthe forthcoming employment tribunal.
OL,11,FHe added: "The recruitment process for
OL,12,Fa permanent Chief Fire Officer or
OL,13,FChief Executive Officer will begin as
OL,14,Fsoon as the commissioners have a clear
OL,15,Fview on the future needs of the
OL,16,Fservice."
